## Design direction (confirmed by research)

orschellx.com confirms: dark background, black/grey/neon orange brand. Rugged working-class identity ("Dirt Hammers", "Keep Banging Em").

| Token | Value |
|---|---|
| Background | `#1C1F24` (dark steel) |
| Surface | `#2B2E35` (mid steel) |
| Card | `#33373F` |
| Accent primary | `#F76B10` (construction orange — matches orschellx.com "flow orange") |
| Accent hi-vis | `#FFD600` (caution yellow) |
| Text primary | `#EAEAEA` |
| Text muted | `#9AA0AB` |
| Danger/Out-of-stock | `#E84040` |
| Success/In-stock | `#27AE60` |
| Headings | "Barlow Condensed" (Google Fonts), bold, uppercase |
| Body | "Inter" (Google Fonts) |
| Motifs | Diagonal hazard-stripe dividers, heavy 2px borders, uppercase pill badges, dense product grid |

