| User auth & account mgmt | JWT signup/login, account page, order history; 2 seeded accounts | Planned |
| Product catalog management | Admin CMS: CRUD products + categories, pricing, specs, featured flag | Planned |
| Inventory tracking | Stock decrements atomically on order; low-stock flags; admin stock edits | Planned |
| Order processing workflows | Cart to checkout to order; admin 4-state status pipeline | Planned |
| Payment gateway integration | Mock checkout, fake card form, success/decline simulation, clearly labeled | Planned |
| REST API development | 22 documented endpoints, proper HTTP codes, admin guards | Planned |
| Performance optimization | Paginated queries, 7 indexes, client-side cart+auth state caching | Planned |
| Database improvements | Relational schema, FKs, CHECK constraints, 7 indexes, seeds | Planned |

---

## Risks and mitigations

| Risk | Mitigation |
|---|---|
| Scope (richness 10, large feature set) | Admin CMS + storefront unified — hero covers all 8 requirements |
| Surface node:sqlite Node 22 check | CLAUDE.md confirms Surface is Node 22; node:sqlite built-in, no gyp |
| Oversell race condition | Atomic UPDATE with quantity >= ? check; CHECK(quantity >= 0) constraint |
| Demo file count cap | Vite bundles frontend to ~3 files; backend on Surface not counted |
| Build timeout | Backend and frontend built in separate Surface runner scripts |

